org.xlattice.corexml.bind

Class SubElBinding

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.xlattice.corexml.bind.Join
      • org.xlattice.corexml.bind.Binding
        • org.xlattice.corexml.bind.SubElBinding

  • public class SubElBinding
extends Binding
    Bind a subelement value in XML to the value of the named field in the associated class. As the term is used here, 'subelement value' means text enclosed by the opening and closing parts of the element, such as 
       <height> 182 cm </height>

    Author:
    Jim Dixon
